This isn't right where we want them.

23:23.486 --> 23:26.781
Well, that's your job now.

23:27.282 --> 23:30.493
- Oh.
MAHONE: This is as far as I go.

23:31.744 --> 23:32.996
Or is it something else?

23:34.706 --> 23:36.291
Another reason we're all here?

23:36.457 --> 23:38.167
Like that.

23:40.295 --> 23:43.298
- Like a double-cross.
- Yeah, just like that. Say goodbye.

23:43.464 --> 23:44.841
[CLATTERING]

23:45.842 --> 23:49.012
Great minds think alike, eh, Alex?

23:52.974 --> 23:54.058
[METAL CLINKS]

23:54.225 --> 23:55.893
[GUNSHOTS]

24:30.845 --> 24:33.222
[GRUNTING]

24:56.746 --> 24:59.666
Okay, come on, come on.

