will be mounted to the floor-mount.

25:18.226 --> 25:20.520
During transport,
do not speak to either I, myself--

25:20.687 --> 25:22.397
I know the drill.

25:25.483 --> 25:27.402
Get in.

25:50.133 --> 25:53.928
MAN: So, what have we got, 3O minutes?
- Yeah, something like that.

25:54.095 --> 25:56.639
- Why didn't you take the freeway?
DRIVER: Rush hour.

25:59.142 --> 26:01.310
- Oh, hell.
MAN: What?

26:01.519 --> 26:05.440
DRIVER: The engine light just came on.
- It just got serviced at motor pool.

26:05.606 --> 26:08.776
Yeah. We've gotta pull over
just to make sure.

26:24.041 --> 26:25.752
All right, I'll check it out.

26:34.010 --> 26:37.346
In the French Resistance, it was
a high honor to face a Nazi firing squad.

26:37.555 --> 26:40.683
- Thought I told you to be quiet.
- Meant you did your job.

26:41.809 --> 26:45.062
The highest honor was to smile
when they shot you.

26:45.229 --> 26:46.647
[DOOR OPENS]

26:47.690 --> 26:49.609
Took you long enough.

27:01.871 --> 27:03.706
MAN:
Lake Gatun. Eastern canal.

27:03.873 --> 27:06.834
Approaches to Cartegena.
Twenty-seven-fifty.

27:07.001 --> 27:08.628
MAHONE:
What's that crossing take?

27:08.795 --> 27:11.714
Two days
if you're under full sail all the time.

27:11.881 --> 27:14.717
Good time of year to be down here.
No storms. Nothing.

27:14.884 --> 27:16.886
Had enough storms recently.

27:17.053 --> 27:20.139
MAN: Enjoy it. It's a beautiful crossing.
MAHONE: Ha-ha. I plan to.

27:20.306 --> 27:22.850
This boat here. Who does it belong to?

27:23.601 --> 27:24.852
Sefior?

27:25.019 --> 27:27.939
We got a call that this boat was used
in some illegal trafficking.

27:28.105 --> 27:31.400
It's the wrong boat, pal.
You can check it if you want to, but--

27:31.609 --> 27:34.737
- Hey, you can't just go to--
- Hey, this is Panama, friend.

27:34.904 --> 27:37.031
Get acquainted with the law, huh?

27:40.117 --> 27:41.994
OFFICER: Coca.

27:43.871 --> 27:47.375
Yes, I definitely think you need
to get acquainted with it.

27:47.542 --> 27:49.460
Chico.

27:51.921 --> 27:54.465
Well, l...

28:02.014 --> 28:04.851
LINCOLN: You think they got him?
MICHAEL: It's a pretty singular boat.

28:05.017 --> 28:08.020
LINCOLN: That's a lot of coke to be
carrying around. If you were at the helm--

28:08.187 --> 28:10.314
I'd be doing some serious time.
Ten years, minimum.

28:10.481 --> 28:13.109
LINCOLN:
Yeah, you would. We lost the boat.

28:13.276 --> 28:15.194
At least we got dead man's money.

28:15.361 --> 28:17.321
It's our ticket
to the rest of our lives...

28:17.488 --> 28:19.907
...minus what I'm sending
Westmoreland's daughter.

28:20.074 --> 28:21.993
Hey-

28:22.827 --> 28:24.996
- You showed up.
- We had a deal.

28:25.663 --> 28:27.456
- That's my brother.
- Hey.

28:27.665 --> 28:29.500
This way.

28:31.085 --> 28:33.671
So we get out of here
and we never look back.

28:34.338 --> 28:36.465
We never look back.

28:42.346 --> 28:45.349
LINCOLN: I wanna thank you, Michael,
for everything.

28:46.684 --> 28:48.519
MICHAEL:
You're welcome.

28:50.396 --> 28:52.773
It's the best I could do
with the money you gave me.

28:53.941 --> 28:55.985
MICHAEL:
That'll work.

28:57.194 --> 28:59.447
[SPEAKING IN SPANISH]

29:01.908 --> 29:05.036
- She's very pretty.
- She'll get us where we need to go?

29:05.202 --> 29:07.371
Not the boat, sefior.

29:31.896 --> 29:33.731
So I got your message.

29:35.441 --> 29:38.069
Thank God I found you guys.

29:40.780 --> 29:42.740
Thank God is right.

29:42.907 --> 29:45.034
Michael, Lincoln's free.

29:45.201 --> 29:46.452
What?

29:46.619 --> 29:51.666
Uh, it's all over the news.
Paul Kellerman came forward.

29:51.832 --> 29:55.419
And he had everything documented
and he made a full confession.

29:55.586 --> 29:58.130
- Are you serious?
- Yeah.

29:58.839 --> 30:01.926
LINCOLN: Everything?
- Everything. All charges.

30:04.220 --> 30:05.680
Whoa.

30:07.765 --> 30:09.976
What a...

30:11.102 --> 30:15.064
Man, what a-- No more...

30:15.231 --> 30:17.692
It means you don't
have to run anymore.

30:21.237 --> 30:23.447
What about Michael?

30:23.614 --> 30:26.617
Uh, a friend of my father's
is getting into it...

30:26.784 --> 30:29.870
...but he's pretty confident
that under the circumstances...

30:30.037 --> 30:32.289
...nobody's gonna pursue you on this.

30:37.628 --> 30:39.797
I need a drink.

30:40.589 --> 30:43.134
I'll go see what I can find.

31:00.818 --> 31:02.528
Here.

31:03.320 --> 31:04.989
Help me out of this.

31:11.328 --> 31:13.414
We did it, Linc.

31:15.374 --> 31:17.376
- We did it.
- Yeah.

31:17.543 --> 31:18.919
KIM:
No.

31:20.504 --> 31:21.756
You almost did it.

31:32.850 --> 31:34.894
LINCOLN:
You want the money?

31:36.270 --> 31:38.189
Take the money. Take it.

31:39.356 --> 31:41.776
You think this is about the money?

31:44.195 --> 31:46.030
Pocket change? Like 5 million?

31:46.197 --> 31:49.200
Then what is it about?
My brother's been exonerated.

31:49.366 --> 31:53.370
The president stepped down.
We're not a threat anymore. It's over.

31:53.954 --> 31:57.208
You may be done with us, but that
doesn't mean we're done with you.

31:57.750 --> 32:01.712
- The police are on their way.
LINCOLN: This started with me.

32:01.879 --> 32:05.633
- Let my brother go.
- Oh, that's sweet, that's sweet.

32:05.800 --> 32:09.887
You don't hear that much anymore,
that sort of fidelity in families.

32:10.012 --> 32:13.474
Two brothers who will go to the ends
of the earth for each other.

32:14.266 --> 32:15.893
Too bad only one of you will survive.

32:16.060 --> 32:17.269
[GUNSHOT]

32:17.436 --> 32:18.479
No!

32:29.907 --> 32:31.909
We gotta go.

32:45.798 --> 32:48.592
[SPEAKING IN SPANISH]

33:48.652 --> 33:53.157
My men have orders to fire if you
don't come out with your hands first.

33:58.621 --> 34:03.125
Murder is not something that we take
lightly here on Panamanian soil.

34:03.292 --> 34:05.878
So come on out of there
and there will be no more deaths.

34:06.045 --> 34:08.505
Michael, I took a man's life.

34:09.297 --> 34:11.425
Don't think about that now.

34:11.592 --> 34:13.928
You and I have got a date, remember?

34:14.094 --> 34:16.554
Two limes and a couple of beers.
Don't forget that.

34:16.722 --> 34:19.099
MAN:
This is your last warning.

34:19.266 --> 34:20.768
Give me the gun.

34:23.603 --> 34:25.022
I took a man's life.

34:27.024 --> 34:31.779
We're gonna walk out of here together
and tell them exactly what happened.

34:31.946 --> 34:33.864
[SARA SOBBING]

34:34.031 --> 34:36.699
No, look at me, look at me,
look at me.

34:37.368 --> 34:39.620
Now, we're gonna tell them
what happened.

34:39.786 --> 34:42.623
- Okay.
- We're gonna explain everything.

34:43.206 --> 34:46.335
And I'm gonna do
whatever I can to help you.

34:46.877 --> 34:50.089
- Okay?
- Yeah.

34:52.925 --> 34:55.135
Now, give me the gun.

34:55.886 --> 34:57.554
Here.

35:04.895 --> 35:06.689
You ready?

35:11.068 --> 35:13.195
SARA:
I love you.

35:15.322 --> 35:17.574
I love you too, Sara.

35:32.923 --> 35:34.174
- Okay.
- You ready?

35:34.341 --> 35:35.676
- Yeah.
- All right.

35:35.843 --> 35:38.262
- Yeah.
- Come on.

35:43.434 --> 35:45.102
Don't move!

35:45.269 --> 35:46.937
I'll shoot!

35:47.104 --> 35:49.606
- Michael, what are you doing?
- Nobody moves! Nobody!

35:51.900 --> 35:54.820
- You sacrificed everything for me once.
- No.

35:54.987 --> 35:58.032
- No! Don't move!
- No, I won't let you do this.

35:58.198 --> 35:59.950
Michael. Michael!

36:00.117 --> 36:04.204
Now it's time to say thank you.
It was me! It was me!

36:04.371 --> 36:06.623
- I did it!
SARA: He's done nothing wrong!

36:06.790 --> 36:10.044
- He's innocent!
- I did it! It was me.

36:10.210 --> 36:12.796
- I did it! It was me.
- He's done nothing wrong.

36:12.963 --> 36:15.716
He hasn't shot anybody,
he hasn't hurt anybody. Michael.

36:15.883 --> 36:17.718
Michael, tell them the truth!

36:17.885 --> 36:21.513
Michael! He's done nothing wrong!

36:41.992 --> 36:44.036
[PHONE RINGS]

36:45.954 --> 36:47.498
Hello?

36:48.707 --> 36:50.000
Hey, it's me.

36:50.167 --> 36:54.171
Oh, getting impatient. Reminds me
of when we were in college.

36:56.340 --> 36:57.841
Did you buy the tickets yet?

36:58.509 --> 37:00.928
<i>No, I'm still looking.</i>

37:01.095 --> 37:02.346
Don't.

37:03.472 --> 37:07.226
- What?
- Forget about them.

37:09.770 --> 37:11.230
Forget I ever existed.

37:11.438 --> 37:12.898
[SNIFFLING]

37:35.712 --> 37:38.715
- Excuse me. You speak English?
- Yes. Can I help you?

37:38.882 --> 37:41.218
Yeah. I'm looking for a woman.
Sara Tancredi.

37:41.385 --> 37:43.762
She was brought in to give her
statement, then released.

37:43.929 --> 37:45.431
You just missed her.

37:54.648 --> 37:55.899
Sara!

38:29.600 --> 38:31.685
Oh, God.

38:32.603 --> 38:34.396
I thought you'd never show up.

38:37.274 --> 38:40.694
Okay, when am I getting out of here?

38:41.487 --> 38:44.740
That's the thing.
There's been a hiccup.

38:44.907 --> 38:45.991
[LAUGHS]

38:46.158 --> 38:47.576
A hiccup?

38:48.118 --> 38:49.661
Look, you guys got me.

38:49.828 --> 38:52.664
You got me fair and square
in Mexico, all right?

38:52.831 --> 38:56.376
I did what you wanted me to do. Now
it's time to cut me loose like we agreed.

38:56.543 --> 38:58.545
Getting caught wasn't part
of the agreement.

38:58.712 --> 39:00.589
I got caught running your setup.

39:01.381 --> 39:03.217
Being your bait.

39:03.383 --> 39:06.303
Now, I got you Scofield down here.
I got you what you wanted.

39:08.555 --> 39:10.474
You got caught, Bagwell.

39:12.518 --> 39:14.603
Wait. Where you going?!

39:14.770 --> 39:16.438
Where you going?

39:16.897 --> 39:20.984
I got you what you wanted!
I got them boys down here!

39:21.151 --> 39:24.112
I did what you told me to do!

39:24.655 --> 39:28.784
Do you hear me?
I did what you told me to do!

39:28.951 --> 39:31.078
I did what you told me!

40:41.273 --> 40:43.900
This is as far as we go.

41:08.842 --> 41:10.552
MAN:
General.

41:13.305 --> 41:16.600
I trust this is a safe place to speak.

41:16.767 --> 41:18.810
It's Scofield.

41:18.977 --> 41:20.937
They got him.

41:38.789 --> 41:41.583
[CHATTERING]

41:59.351 --> 42:01.728
Scofield back in the pen.

42:01.895 --> 42:05.857
Gotta be honest,
I didn't think we'd see it happen.

42:07.359 --> 42:09.361
You know he's gonna break out.

42:09.528 --> 42:11.738
It's in his blood.

42:12.781 --> 42:15.867
That's exactly what
we want him to do.

43:59.846 --> 44:01.932
[ENGLISH SDH]
